  </a></h3>
  <p>These tools are designed to help schools work with parents from diverse cultures to support the family&rsquo;s engagement in their child&rsquo;s education.&nbsp; Tools are provided to help parents support their child&rsquo;s academic performance, become more informed decision makers about their child&rsquo;s education, and improve home-school communication and partnership. The tools for parents are also available in Spanish, Hmong and Somali. </p></td>
